    "body": "EpMoE on Blackwell with deepgemm currently fails with the following error due to the absence of get_col_major_tma_aligned_tensor:\r\n\r\n``` \r\n File \"/sgl-workspace/sglang/python/sglang/srt/layers/moe/ep_moe/layer.py\", line 204, in forward_deepgemm\r\n    deep_gemm_wrapper.get_col_major_tma_aligned_tensor(gateup_input_scale),\r\n    ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\nAttributeError: module 'sglang.srt.layers.quantization.deep_gemm_wrapper' has no attribute 'get_col_major_tma_aligned_tensor'\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis PR addresses the issue by adding the missing function or ensuring compatibility with Blackwell deepgemm.\r\n\r\ncc. @kushanam @zhyncs ",
